                        <span class="tag">NLP</span>
                        <span class="tag">PyTorch</span>
                        <span class="tag">Python</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Project 2 -->
            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-content">
                    <h3>Real-time Object Detection</h3>
                    <p>Implemented a YOLOv8-based pipeline to detect and track safety equipment on construction sites with 92% mAP (mean Average Precision).</p>
                    <div class="tags">
                        <span class="tag">Computer Vision</span>
                        <span class="tag">OpenCV</span>
                        <span class="tag">Deep Learning</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Project 3 -->
            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-content">
                    <h3>Customer Churn Prediction</h3>
                    <p>Developed a predictive model using Gradient Boosting (LightGBM) to identify at-risk customers, improving retention by 15% in a pilot study.</p>
                    <div class="tags">
                        <span class="tag">Machine Learning</span>
                        <span class="tag">SQL</span>
                        <span class="tag">Pandas</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="education" class="container">
        <h2>Education & Certifications</h2>
        <div class="edu-item">
            <div class="edu-meta">2020 — 2024</div>
            <h3>B.S. in Computer Science (AI Specialization)</h3>
            <p>University Name | GPA: 3.8/4.0</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="edu-item">
            <div class="edu-meta">Certified 2025</div>
            <h3>Deep Learning Specialization (DeepLearning.AI)</h3>
            <p>Coursera Certification</p>
        </div>

        <div class="edu-item">
            <div class="edu-meta">Certified 2024</div>
            <h3>AWS Certified Machine Learning – Specialty</h3>
            <p>Amazon Web Services</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="container">
        <h2>Contact Information</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">I am currently open to full-time opportunities and collaborations.</p>
        <div class="contact-links">
            <a href="mailto:your.email@example.com" class="contact-item">📧 your.email@email.com</a>
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourusername" target="_blank" class="contact-item">🔗 LinkedIn</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/yourusername" target="_blank" class="contact-item">💻 GitHub</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2026 [Your Name]. Built for the future of AI.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Smooth scrolling for navigation links
        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({
                    behavior: 'smooth'
                });
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
